This package contains the java source code and binaries for the Segmented 
Topic Model (STM) described in:

Lan Du, Wray Buntine and Huidong Jin, "A segmented topic model based on the 
two-parameter Poisson-Dirichlet process", Mach. Learn., 81(1):5â€“19.


